{
  "stem": "15694.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On top of that, they took in-- the husband took in the brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a fellow who in my imagination looked like a hero, but he didn't do any heroic things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he did something else for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He organized-- now, hard to believe in those days-- card games.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- they played for high stakes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a game similar to poker, only with four cards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's called-- called euchre.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when the kitty was rather high, and it was decided who would be winning it yet, he took a note away for my mother, who provided them with tea and cakes and whatever, what have you.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father must have be sort of amazed that suddenly instead of worrying about us, his food got better, what we sent him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had money as never before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But as I say, the screw of oppression was turning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then suddenly, we had to go-- they renamed the place where we lived Adolf Hitler Platz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And of course, Jews have to leave it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were sent to a place which probably was later the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I can't remember the street name anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I can't even remember the family where we stayed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well-- and at this family, I don't know whether they were voluntary giving us the place, or was it because-- well, the Jewish-- the Jewish community-- Jewish council forced them already to do that.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
